# Prompt: Implement Global Command Palette (Ctrl + K) & Favorite Tools for phung.work
## Objective
Implement two global productivity features for **phung.work**:
1. Global Command Palette (Ctrl + K)
2. Favorite Tools
The experience should be comparable to:
* Raycast
* VS Code Command Palette
* Linear
* Vercel Dashboard
* GitHub Command Menu
* Notion Quick Search
These features should work across the entire website and integrate seamlessly with the existing design system.
Do not change the existing routing architecture unless necessary.
